<span id="freeTextContainer3515120991194836871">What a lovely story. This is my first Sherri Hayes book, and I am looking forward to reading more. The characters were well developed, and their pasts heart breaking. The love story was very real and sweet. And it was all accomplished without the cheese that usually accompanies these types of books.<br/><br/>The supporting cast was also great. I loved the Daniels Clan, and Jan, and even the persistent detective. <br/><br/>I can&apos;t wait for the next installment of this series!<br/><br/></span>
